---
title: Mexican Black Bean Burrito Bowl with Leafy Rice & Avocado
description: Embark on a culinary fiesta with our Mexican burrito bowl, where black beans are simmered in a tomato-based sauce and served alongside a mild avocado salsa and cooling sour cream. This vibrant bowl is a symphony of flavours, delivering a taste of Mexico in every satisfying bite!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66e21ecb0044b6239a87ef5d-c2203199.jpeg
